{"id": 2159, "genre": 1001, "title": "父母教育你的方式，哪些你暗暗想过绝不会再带给自己的孩子？", "description": "“如果你在用正确的方式养育孩子，养育孩子的确就是很辛苦的。”——美国论坛 Reddit 用户 @hgmnynow（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 6916, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180201180536xcb4T2y8XFaet7pU.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-02T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 263168, "content": "讽刺，谩骂，大喊大叫，还美其名曰“良药苦口” 想说这真是我听过的最蠢的谎话，low就是low,改就是了，找什么借口？", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 785128}, {"id": 263424, "content": "如图", "image": "img/option/option/20180203132347hTDUb342yi7ez51B.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187001}, {"id": 263936, "content": "小时候父母的打骂\n高中时的不尊重\n工作时的逼婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256529}, {"id": 263169, "content": "和别的小朋友吵架的时候，不管三七二十一反正都是我不对，为了不破坏他们大人表面的和气", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1252586}, {"id": 263425, "content": "不会推心置腹的聊天。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253499}, {"id": 263937, "content": "被和‘别人家孩子’的各种比较！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914981}, {"id": 263170, "content": "从不对你进行肯定，告诉你别人可比你强多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1252592}, {"id": 263426, "content": "太冒险的事情，就不要做了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1252613}, {"id": 263171, "content": "所谓穷养孩子，就是要把没钱的压力推给孩子。这个不能买，因为咱家没钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 210, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107047}, {"id": 263683, "content": "等你自己当了父母以后就理解我们了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234521}, {"id": 264195, "content": "当着孩子的面跟别人说自己孩子的坏话，一点都不遮掩。\n一味的强制，用脾气教育", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257750}, {"id": 263172, "content": "我们这辛苦做什么都是为了你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1237071}, {"id": 263428, "content": "看了很多，感觉大致就是以后做一个佛系父母就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174431}, {"id": 265220, "content": "不思进取，不求成长，不接受任何批评和建议无论自己做得对与否，用找借口推卸责任来证明自己没有任何问题，做错事情也绝对不道歉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262341}, {"id": 263173, "content": "你看看谁谁家的小孩，你不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107047}, {"id": 263429, "content": "不要跟人比穿什么，吃什么，过得怎么样，跟人比学习。", "image": "img/option/option/20180203144055FpZbQI7dyXJtzN3C", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253539}, {"id": 263174, "content": "不会换位思考。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650722}, {"id": 263430, "content": "不会用自己的世界观和意识强加给小孩，不怕尝试后的错误，鼓励多于告诉你这个世界有很多危机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253524}, {"id": 263175, "content": "冷嘲热讽的打击", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249418}, {"id": 263176, "content": "发生争吵时永远都是你不懂事，不理解父母的难处。", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179384}, {"id": 263177, "content": "女孩子一定要要强，我们没发给你更多需要你自己去拼去争", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036953}, {"id": 263433, "content": "把抚养孩子的义务加在祖辈或其他人身上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253556}, {"id": 263178, "content": "离爸爸妈妈近一点总是好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1252613}, {"id": 263434, "content": "父母和孩子之间交流过少，因为忙于工作而疏忽孩子小时候的陪伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198266}, {"id": 263436, "content": "在不了解原因的情况下直接开骂，了解之后不道歉", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220355}, {"id": 263438, "content": "除了学习，不允许它有别的爱好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096161}, {"id": 263183, "content": "别人家的孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028920}, {"id": 263439, "content": "被我妈打到自残看到伤口还粉刺我", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253573}, {"id": 263184, "content": "总是以自己那个时代的价值观和思想教育你 不懂时代是变化的...", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215613}, {"id": 263440, "content": "毫无意识的以为是防止孩子不谦虚的非鼓励式教育，即时偶尔在别人的肯定前作为家长会有所同感，同样肯定孩子，但此时作为孩子对比家长一贯的无鼓励，还蛮心理叛逆跟失落的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 884286}, {"id": 263185, "content": "长大以后一定要结婚 一定要生孩子 一定要是异性...", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215613}, {"id": 263186, "content": "完全放养式教育孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224651}, {"id": 263698, "content": "不是这个社会怎么样，孩子就该怎么样，沟通还是最重要的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210065}, {"id": 263188, "content": "他做事情做的不好，或者不对，会耐心教他鼓励他。不是一味的骂他傻啊笨啊，自己解气了就不理他，把孩子当出气筒", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1180170}, {"id": 263189, "content": "在孩子面前数落对方的不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1252544}, {"id": 263445, "content": "这个考试会考吗？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358363}, {"id": 263190, "content": "大声呵斥", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1252625}, {"id": 263446, "content": "根本就不想生养孩子了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235507}, {"id": 263191, "content": "不孝有三，那啥为大...", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775953}, {"id": 263192, "content": "不以爱之名束缚孩子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775953}, {"id": 263448, "content": "除了学习，什么事情都不要管。\n不要跟学习不好的同学在一起。\n永远把你当作思想上的孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253633}, {"id": 264728, "content": "逃不掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259729}, {"id": 263193, "content": "不把别人家的孩子作为比较标准。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775953}, {"id": 263449, "content": "不倾听", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120812}, {"id": 263450, "content": "  总是说自己文化低，并以此为借口将所有错都带过\n  认为大人说的话全是正确的，小孩应该无条件听从大人的，因为小孩不懂事。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155797}, {"id": 263195, "content": "陪伴少，说教多，言行不一", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132422}, {"id": 263196, "content": "厌恶的眼神", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219821}, {"id": 263197, "content": "棍法", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230174}, {"id": 263198, "content": "没有问过他，就给他上各种各样的兴趣班", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609712}, {"id": 265246, "content": "他们做的决定都是为我好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262513}]}